    <title type="html"><![CDATA[MSSQL无法添加数据连接]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.youth2009.org/blog/2011/12/13/mssql-can-not-add-data-link/"/>
    <updated>2011-12-13T19:10:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://www.youth2009.org/blog/2011/12/13/mssql-can-not-add-data-link</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code>        &lt;p&gt;“无法添加数据连接。未能加载文件或程序集“Microsoft SqlServer.Management.Sdk.sfc,Version=10.0.0.0,Culture=nutral,publicKey=89845dcd8080cc91"或它的某一个依赖项。系统找不到指定的文件。”&lt;/p&gt;
</code></pre>

<p>今下午卸载了SQL2008，然后装了2005，在VS2010中使用SqlDataSource的时候发现无法创建数据库连接，错误就是这样说的，我现在猜想可能是卸载SQL2008的时候多卸载了一些东西。</p>


<p>于是下载了下面这两个东西装上后就没问题了：</p>


<p>感谢<a href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_62fd44430100zccr.html">这位</a>（我直接复制了他的内容）</p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">（1）<strong style="font-weight: bold;">Microsoft SQL Server 系统 CLR 类型</strong></p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">SQL Server 系统 CLR 类型包中包含用于在 SQL Server 2008 中实现新的 geometry、geography 和 hierarchyid 类型的组件。此组件可与服务器分开安装，以允许客户端应用程序在服务器之外使用这些类型。</p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;">注意：</strong>此组件还要求有 <strong style="font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #905032;" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=123373"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; color: #78afd3;">Windows Installer 4.5</span></a></strong>。</p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">用户：<strong style="font-weight: bold;">客户、合作伙伴、开发人员</strong></p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #905032;" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=123721&amp;clcid=0x804"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; color: #78afd3;">X86 包</span></a></strong> (SQLSysClrTypes.msi) - 1588 KB<br /><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #905032;" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=123722&amp;clcid=0x804"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; color: #78afd3;">X64 包</span></a></strong> (SQLSysClrTypes.msi) - 1981 KB<br /><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #905032;" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=123724&amp;clcid=0x804"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; color: #78afd3;">IA64 包</span></a></strong> (SQLSysClrTypes.msi) - 3289 KB</p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">（2）<strong style="font-weight: bold;">Microsoft SQL Server 2008 管理对象</strong></p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">SQL Server 管理对象 (SMO) 是一个 .NET Framework 对象模型，软件开发人员使用该模型可以创建用于管理 SQL Server 对象和服务的客户端应用程序。此对象模型将与 SQL Server 2000、SQL Server 2005 和 SQL Server 2008 协同工作。</p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;">注意：</strong>Microsoft SQL Server 2008 管理对象集合需要安装 <strong style="font-weight: bold;">Microsoft Core XML Services (MSXML) 6.0</strong> 和 Microsoft SQL Server Native Client，本页中也提供了这两个程序。</p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">用户：<strong style="font-weight: bold;">客户、合作伙伴、开发人员</strong></p>


<p style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: #464646; font-family: simsun; text-align: left; background-color: #e8dcc8; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #905032;" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=123708&amp;clcid=0x804"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; color: #78afd3;">X86 包</span></a></strong> (SharedManagementObjects.msi) - 3225 KB<br /><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #905032;" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=123709&amp;clcid=0x804"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; color: #78afd3;">X64 包</span></a></strong> (SharedManagementObjects.msi) - 3895 KB<br /><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #905032;" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=123710&amp;clcid=0x804"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; color: #78afd3;">IA64 包</span></a></strong> (SharedManagementObjects.msi) - 5640 KB</p>

